OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782411505
OL,3,CJulia Donaldson sends good wishes to
OL,4,CHartlepool school in global prize
OL,5,Cshortlist
OL,7,FChildren's author Julia Donaldson has
OL,8,Fcongratulated a Hartlepool school
OL,9,Fwhich has been shortlisted for a
OL,10,Fglobal education prize.
OL,12,FWard Jackson Church of England Primary
OL,13,FSchool is among five UK schools in the
OL,14,Ftop 10 list for the World's Best
OL,15,FSchool Prizes this year.
OL,17,FIn a video message, The Gruffalo
OL,18,Fcreator sent her good wishes to the
OL,19,Fpupils at Ward Jackson.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
