PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782411505
OL,3,CJulia Donaldson sends good wishes to
OL,4,CHartlepool school in global prize
OL,5,Cshortlist
OL,7,FShe said: "Congratulations, that's a
OL,8,Fhuge achievement for quite a small
OL,9,Fschool and I was also very pleased to
OL,10,Fhear you like my stories, not just
OL,11,Fthat you like reading them but I hear
OL,12,Fyou've been acting them and drawing
OL,13,Fthem and getting to really know the
OL,14,Fcharacters so that's great as well."
OL,16,FThe five World's Best School Prizes
OL,17,Fwas founded by T4 Education in 2022
OL,18,Fand have been described as the 'World
OL,19,FCup for Schools', created to share the
OL,20,Fbest practices in education settings.
OL,26,@oD@KOUvD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
