PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782411505
OL,3,CJulia Donaldson sends good wishes to
OL,4,CHartlepool school in global prize
OL,5,Cshortlist
OL,7,FWard Jackson is a state-funded primary
OL,8,Fschool with 70% of its students
OL,9,Faffected by poverty. It has been named
OL,10,Fin the top 10 shortlist for the
OL,11,Fawards' Overcoming Adversity category.
OL,13,FJonathan Brash, MP for Hartlepool,
OL,14,Fpraised the school, saying: "This is a
OL,15,Ftruly remarkable achievement and
OL,16,Feveryone associated with Ward Jackson
OL,17,FSchool should be immensely proud.
OL,26,@vD@]OU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
