OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782411505
OL,3,CJulia Donaldson sends good wishes to
OL,4,CHartlepool school in global prize
OL,5,Cshortlist
OL,7,F"To be recognised among the top ten
OL,8,Fschools in the world in the Overcoming
OL,9,FAdversity category of the World's Best
OL,10,FSchool Prizes is an extraordinary
OL,11,Faccolade and one that shines a
OL,12,Fspotlight not only on the school, but
OL,13,Fon the values and ambitions of our
OL,14,Ftown.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782411505
OL,3,CJulia Donaldson sends good wishes to
OL,4,CHartlepool school in global prize
OL,5,Cshortlist
OL,7,F"At a time when the Government is
OL,8,Frightly focused on breaking down
OL,9,Fbarriers to opportunity, Ward Jackson
OL,10,Fstands as a national example of what
OL,11,Fcan be achieved when schools combine
OL,12,Fhigh expectations with genuine care
OL,13,Fand inclusion. The school has been
OL,14,Frefining this model for years and the
OL,15,Fresults speak for themselves."
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
