OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782411505
OL,3,CJulia Donaldson sends good wishes to
OL,4,CHartlepool school in global prize
OL,5,Cshortlist
OL,7,FMr Brash paid tribute to the school's
OL,8,Fstaff, parents and pupils, adding:
OL,9,F"Ward Jackson is not just one of the
OL,10,Fbest schools in our region. It is now
OL,11,Fbeing recognised as one of the best
OL,12,Fexamples in the world of how education
OL,13,Fcan transform lives. I sincerely hope
OL,14,Fministers take notice because if there
OL,15,Fis a flagship model for overcoming
OL,16,Fadversity and raising aspiration, Ward
OL,17,FJackson School has made a compelling
OL,18,Fcase to be it."
OL,26,@qD@AOUzD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
