OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782411505
OL,3,CJulia Donaldson sends good wishes to
OL,4,CHartlepool school in global prize
OL,5,Cshortlist
OL,7,FVikas Pota, founder of T4 Education
OL,8,Fand the prize, said the five settings
OL,9,Fhave shown that "British schools truly
OL,10,Fstand among the best in the world".
OL,12,FThe winners will be chosen by an
OL,13,Fexpert panel and the top three
OL,14,Ffinalists and winners will be
OL,15,Fannounced in November.
OL,26,@qD@QOUrD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/8
