PN,39408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782411505
OL,3,CJulia Donaldson sends good wishes to
OL,4,CHartlepool school in global prize
OL,5,Cshortlist
OL,7,FWinners and shortlisted schools will
OL,8,Fthen be invited to the World Schools
OL,9,FSummit in London in January 2027 where
OL,10,Fthey will share what they do with
OL,11,Fpolicymakers and leading figures in
OL,12,Fglobal education.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/8
